snippet.title: Jason Momoa Reveals Nobody Likes Amber Heard on The Set of Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
Jason Momoa Reveals Nobody Likes Amber Heard on The Set of Aquaman 2! 
Amber Heard was dismissed from Aquaman 2 for a reason, according to Jason Momoa. Jason Mamoa has been making waves in the entertainment industry for quite some time. Indeed, he has been the talk of Hollywood since the release of Aquaman earlier this year, and he has been cast in a variety of parts in a number of projects, leading us to wonder. The next time we see this hottie on the big screen will be in 2022, thanks to Aquaman's amazing popularity immediately after its debut.
